1. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper proposes a recommendation system for music, which falls under the domain of information retrieval. 
2. cs.SD (Sound) - The paper deals with music audio content and proposes a model for music auto-tagging, which falls under the domain of sound. 
3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper deals with user-item interaction and recommendation, which can be considered as a social network problem. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a deep learning-based model for recommendation and auto-tagging tasks. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with music audio content and proposes a model for music auto-tagging, which falls under the domain of multimedia.
